  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<b>义士壮举：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/id-46992__sort_key-agree_count__sort-DESC\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/id-46992__sort_key-agree_count__sort-DESC\">https://pincong.rocks/article/id-46992__sort_key-agree_count__sort-DESC</a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n彭载舟义士于2022年10月13日在北京举事之前有在researchgate留下《罢课罢工罢免习近平攻略》，更多信息可以查看<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9tb2JpbGUudHdpdHRlci5jb20vbGlmYV9QZXR0ZXI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/lifa_Petter\">彭载舟的推特</a>。<br/>\n内容较多，建议直接跳到页尾评论区，需要查看原文的，欢迎在researchgate下载。<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmVzZWFyY2hnYXRlLm5ldC9wdWJsaWNhdGlvbi8zNjQzMDU4MjlfYmFrZWJhZ29uZ2JhbWlhbnhpamlucGluZ2dvbmdl\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/364305829_bakebagongbamianxijinpinggonge\">原文地址</a>【<b>注：现在是北京时间2022年10月14日02:10:54，原文链接已失效，彭载舟推特上回复中国数字时代的推文（见下图）也已删除，推测是中共胁迫的结果。</b>新的链接如下：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9kcml2ZS5nb29nbGUuY29tL2ZpbGUvZC8xeXYzemtWZDhsM1VDLUQwWTZMLVAwaUdnSWVoUk1Fb08vdmlldz91c3A9c2hhcmluZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yv3zkVd8l3UC-D0Y6L-P0iGgIehRMEoO/view?usp=sharing\">新的地址</a>】<br/>\n<br/>\n彭载舟回复中国数字时代的推特：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzhhZTYzZjBkNzA0MzVhNTA4NDljLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/78ae63f0d70435a50849c.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/78ae63f0d70435a50849c.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/78ae63f0d70435a50849c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n以下为全文内容：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjM1MzVkYTQyOWY4NWYxZDE3ZTlkLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f3535da429f85f1d17e9d.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/